front end==== user interface

backend ====== server site

static and dynamic site


          
            BOX MODEL
key to box model is ==== Margin and Padding
===Margin is space in between two independent entities... external space
===Padding is when a parent element is shifting or creating space between itself and the child element.
but if the child element is shifting from the parent element, its called margin...
3 values in padding signifies=== top, right and left, 
4 values signifies === top, right, bottom, left.

WIREFRAME/MURKUP/LAYOUT

ASSIGNMENT
==== WORK ON FOOTER===
width of container = 1050

FORM ELEMENTS
==for collection of data using front end
form action= the route we use to collect and send data to the backend
form method=(POST or GEt) backend also. how the data should be displayed.
input type= input is a text field
name attribute== snake casing(first_name) or camel casing(firstName). 
this attribute is used to draw out data from the backend.
Size== number of characters for a text field
maxlength==limited number of characters to be entered
option value== to send the value to the database.
 we always give transition on d normal state of an image and not the hover state

